-02T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"咁講啦<br />\n張敬軒呢幾年爬到咁高<br />\n娛樂界嚟講<br />\n佢咁嘅地位咁嘅人脈<br />\n佢唔幫手仲要去護旗真係好垃圾<br />\n當年仲識得偷偷地開 IG 撐雨革<br />\n今日今日上咗位<br />\n竟然俾以前更加怕事<br />\n完全冇幫過手之餘<br />\n仲要走去護旗？<br />\n<br />\nWith great power comes great responsibility<br />\n呢幾年賺咗咁多香港人嘅錢<br />\n關鍵時刻完全唔做嘢我已經好失望<br />\n仲要護旗真係好撚垃圾<br />\n何韻詩做緊乜，佢做緊乜？<br />\n久唔久 IG 講半句打下卡<br />\n仲廢過我個港豬同事<br />\n咁就想留住 fans？<br />\n<br />\n今時今日港共不兩立<br />\n一係撐共一係撐港<br />\n咩好多利益怕害人唔表態<br />\n咁又走去做護旗手？<br />\n沈旭暉都表態啦屌你老母<br />\n沈旭暉識啲人夠唔夠勁夠唔夠紅啊？<br />\n<br />\n與其買佢碟睇佢演唱會<br />\n我不如拎啲錢去捐星火買 gear？<br />\n拎去印小熊維尼滿地痴都唔益佢啦"},{"pid":"e84fea6856d2fe58f6582d6bbc7d5f8d6f473c0a","tid":1611904,"uid":73728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"639f87b3c6497d3d71e9e1bf629bf29b4d6b08dd","tid":1611904,"uid":303692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"90c0eda4ec7c80eceb9292afb541b53342f7ff58","tid":1611904,"uid":73728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"好多人話係經紀人 但講真如果藝人本身自己都好抗拒 經理人都吹佢唔脹 你睇下ali 仲要係跟cctvb"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"好明顯ig本人先係佢啦 但係隔離post又屌佢鬧fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"係 串過馬撚"},{"pid":"3dbb0bc7e7c00cfe27a049b370d95335ce626824","tid":1611904,"uid":303692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94d9b15c8e55c0cf45287db334db4efc95fedea","tid":1611904,"uid":28759,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"448a4adf50a2a6355e95343fcc7db97e70fe83d2","tid":1611904,"uid":303692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b981a1a88073854787bed0edbbc9c01a8153a7c9","tid":1611904,"uid":28759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:4